00:00:11,723 --> 00:00:15,058
UNK

2
00:00:15,148 --> 00:00:20,494
UNK

3
00:00:20,494 --> 00:00:23,360
UNK

4
00:00:29,526 --> 00:00:36,961
haynt dem tsvontsikstn april fun toyznt nayn hundert zeks un nayntsikstn yor,

5
00:00:36,985 --> 00:00:42,617
ikh Roze Bilauskinye nem intervyu bay Meyshn Geguzhinski.

6
00:00:42,617 --> 00:00:47,540
Vilne, Lite, di shprakh yidish.

7
00:00:50,890 --> 00:00:53,567
mayn nomen iz Meyshe Geguzhinski.

8
00:00:53,826 --> 00:01:00,789
ikh bin geboyrn gevorn in toyznt nayn hundert fir un tsvontsikstn yor, eyn un tsvontsikstn yanvar in Kovne.

9
00:01:01,774 --> 00:01:04,620
itst bin ikh shoyn alt tsvey un zibetsik yor.

10
00:01:05,352 --> 00:01:09,514
shoyn a tsayt shoyn do gemakht ale rishn, shvern lebn.

11
00:01:10,127 --> 00:01:14,694
ikh volt gezogt, a tragishn un kemferishn lebn.

12
00:01:17,063 --> 00:01:20,111
ikh bin geboyrn in UNK ikh bin geboyrn in Kovne,

13
00:01:20,708 --> 00:01:27,570
bay di eltern, mayn foter hot geheysn Aron Geguzhinski, mayn muter Tema Geguzhinski.

14
00:01:27,711 --> 00:01:36,867
ven ikh volt dort geven fir finf yor, gedenk ikh az der foter hot dort gehat an eygenem kleynem magazintshik.

15
00:01:37,684 --> 00:01:42,825
er hot gehandlt mit farsheydene papirosn,

16
00:01:43,371 --> 00:01:46,605
un nokh azelkhene skhoyres, velkhe

17
00:01:46,695 --> 00:01:50,649
es hot im nit gepast afile dem fakh. velkhe dem zayn fakh iz geven

18
00:01:50,649 --> 00:01:58,653
a meb- a ⟨medmim⟩ arbeter, a mebl arbeter fun veykhn mebl velkhe er hot bakumen zayendik in gefangenshaft

19
00:01:58,761 --> 00:02:03,373
in Daytshland, hot er zikh oysgelernt als zeyer a guter shpetsyalist fun meykh- veykhn mebl.

20
00:02:03,373 --> 00:02:10,039
nor azoy vi er hot gekrogn azoy tsu zogn fun di mamen, fun di fun zayn froy, a nadn, a kleyne kremele,

21
00:02:10,039 --> 00:02:13,183
hot er zikh mit dem farnumen. nor s'im nit gegangen.

22
00:02:14,978 --> 00:02:18,532
er hot ge⟨UNK⟩ dem gantsn lebn hot getroymt tsu forn in Amerike.

23
00:02:19,146 --> 00:02:26,177
in yents a tsayt hobn a sakh yidn, un nit nor yidn, getrakht tsu farbesern dem zeyer lebn,

24
00:02:26,368 --> 00:02:32,471
un avekforn in a groyser land, in a a groys frayer land, un dortn makhn a karyere.

25
00:02:34,350 --> 00:02:39,947
in zayn gesheftl iz im gornit gegangen derfar vos er hot kentik in der yene tsayt nit gekent handlen.

26
00:02:40,645 --> 00:02:47,304
er hot gehandlt mit azelkhene zakhn vi papirosn un in der tsayt, in yener, in Vil- in in Lite,

27
00:02:47,344 --> 00:02:51,134
hot men oyf papirosn gedarft hobn a shpetsyeln erloybenish.

28
00:02:51,529 --> 00:02:55,100
un er hot ⟨got⟩ mit dem gehandlt. in a gutn tog hobn zikh arayngekhapt

29
00:02:57,013 --> 00:03:05,293
fun fin- fun fin- fin-inspektorn. zey hobn untergekhapt zen di papirosn un hobn mit a groysn groyser shtrof bashtroft im, un farmakht dem gesheft.

30
00:03:06,649 --> 00:03:10,220
oyf vifl ikh gedenk, ikh bin ot o alt geven bay finf zeks yor, finf yor,

31
00:03:10,935 --> 00:03:17,611
hot er bashlosn nemen di gantse mishpokhe un ariberforn in a kleyninke shtetl Raseyn. in Lite.

32
00:03:19,845 --> 00:03:27,343
dortn hot er getrakht vet efsher, er fun dortn vet men shoyn laykhter ven geven avektsuforn in Amerike.

33
00:03:27,343 --> 00:03:29,441
vayl er hot gemeynt az di ortike

34
00:03:30,932 --> 00:03:37,811
finantsiner fin- finantsier opteylungen veln nit veln nit veln nit kenen veln nit gefinen zeyer shrtrof vos er darf batsoln.

35
00:03:38,442 --> 00:03:44,679
nor leyder hot er hot men fun fun Raseyn oykh nit aroysgelozn un mir zaynen geblibn lebn in Raseyn.

36
00:03:45,613 --> 00:03:50,095
dortn in Raseyn hobn mir gelebt etlekhe yor,

37
00:03:50,541 --> 00:03:54,883
er hot er hot zikh ayngeor- er hot er hot zikh aynge⟨oret⟩ als zayn als shoyn bay zayn fakh.

38
00:03:54,883 --> 00:04:02,752
als mebl mebl arbeter, un ikh hob un ikh bin avek in yidishe in a hebreishe folkshul.

39
00:04:03,737 --> 00:04:07,426
ikh hob ongehoybn fun ershtn klas farshteyt zikh, vifl ikh gedenk,

40
00:04:11,398 --> 00:04:15,611
ven ikh bin ven ikh ven ikh bin arayn in ershtn klas hob ikh shoyn gekent gut yidish.

41
00:04:16,039 --> 00:04:23,306
ikh hob shoyn geleyent farsheydene bikhelekh oyf yidish. ikh mit mayn bruderl flegn zitsn un durkhleyenen, gedenk ikh, dem bikhele

42
00:04:23,869 --> 00:04:28,874
Andersen's bikhele vegn di tragedye fun Nelo in Portrash,

43
00:04:29,168 --> 00:04:33,178
velkhe hot mir zeyer UNK zeyer shtark zeyer shtark baumruikt di tragedye.

44
00:04:33,285 --> 00:04:38,189
ikh hob geleyent nokh farsheydene, fun di Grininke Beymelekh iz geven a yidishn a yidisher bikhl,

45
00:04:38,247 --> 00:04:40,401
velkhe hot aroysgelozn Helene Khatskeles.

46
00:04:45,148 --> 00:04:50,998
un ven ikh bin shoyn geg- arayngegangen in ershtn klas, bin ikh shoyn geven a guter shiler.

47
00:04:51,072 --> 00:04:54,610
ikh fleg krign ale finfn vayl ikh hob shoyn gekent zeyer gut di yidishe shprakh,

48
00:04:54,615 --> 00:05:00,448
un ikh hob zikh funandergeklibn in yidishe oysyes, kho- kho- khotsh mir hobn dan gelernt hebreish.

49
00:05:05,618 --> 00:05:12,851
in Raseyn hobn mir gelebt bizn yor, oyber zogndik rikhtik,

50
00:05:16,249 --> 00:05:19,415
biz nayn un tsvontsikstn yor. biz nayn un tsvonts- oder draysikstn yor.

51
00:05:19,759 --> 00:05:24,861
un mir zey hobn bashlosn, azoy vi Raseyn iz geven a kleyne shle- sh- a kleyne shtetele, mayn foter hot zikh

52
00:05:24,861 --> 00:05:30,519
hot hot gekrogn farkrig- bakumen dort zeyer veynik arbet, hot er bashlosn aribertsuforn tsurik in Kovne.

53
00:05:31,943 --> 00:05:35,632
undzer lebn iz geven a gemeyner azoy tsu zogn, an oremer,

54
00:05:36,212 --> 00:05:43,310
m'iz ariber in a sht- in ariber in Kovne lebn in a in a sh- in hinter in a forshtot fun Kovne vos heyst Slabodke.

55
00:05:45,595 --> 00:05:49,031
in Slabodke iz geven a shul, a hebreishe shul,

56
00:05:49,290 --> 00:05:52,822
vu ikh hob ongehoybn vu ikh hob forge- forgezetst mayn lernen.

57
00:05:52,822 --> 00:06:00,371
tsvey yor hob ikh gelernt in Raseyn, un in dritn klas bin ikh arayngegangen in dem in a hebreishe shul, zi hot geheysn Bardon's shul.

58
00:06:01,322 --> 00:06:07,576
Bardon iz geven a gevezener direktor fun dem shul, a der- der der der shafer fun di shul,

59
00:06:09,793 --> 00:06:14,529
un zi geven di eyntsike hebreishe shul in Slabodker gegnt.

60
00:06:16,881 --> 00:06:24,081
un ikh ken nor dermonen vegn dem az Bardon hot gehat a tokhter Bardonayke, a bakante revolutsyonerke,

61
00:06:24,137 --> 00:06:26,156
velkhe iz geven shpeter Shmyetskush's froy.

62
00:06:27,597 --> 00:06:30,493
nor in mir mit Bardonen iz nit oysgekumen tsum lernen.

63
00:06:30,634 --> 00:06:33,058
mayn lerer iz geven Yisroel Kaplen.

64
00:06:33,520 --> 00:06:41,799
dos iz geven a vunderbarer pedagog, a posheter mentsh, un er hot zeyer lib gehat zayne kinder, di shiler.

65
00:06:46,041 --> 00:06:57,796
er hot mir gegebn di ershte visn fun natur-visnshaft, fun matematik, fun hebreishe shprakh.

66
00:06:59,035 --> 00:07:02,727
nor di shul hot in gantsn gehat zeks klasn.

67
00:07:02,727 --> 00:07:04,462
ikh hob geendikt di zeks klasn,

68
00:07:05,380 --> 00:07:09,975
un mir zenen ariber lebn in Kovnish- in shoyn in tsenter shtot vu ikh bin arayn

69
00:07:09,975 --> 00:07:15,465
lernen shoyn in di in a in a shul in a folkshul, Kov- Tarbut shul, hebreishe Tarbut shul.

70
00:07:16,433 --> 00:07:22,839
di Tarbut shul iz geven nit vayt fun undzer dort vu mir hobn gelebt,

71
00:07:25,208 --> 00:07:29,167
der direktor iz dortn geven Kharit, zi hot zikh gerufn di Kharit shul.

72
00:07:34,675 --> 00:07:37,875
un di klasn dertsierin hot geheysn Shifmanovitsh.

73
00:07:47,449 --> 00:07:54,159
in der shul hob ikh hob ongehoybn tsu lernen fun finftn klas, bizn ende, bizn zekstn klas.

74
00:07:54,520 --> 00:07:56,758
ikh ken nit, ikh gedenk nokh aza min kuryoz

75
00:07:56,950 --> 00:08:00,369
ven mir hobn gemakht shtrayk. bay undz iz geven a lerer Gimant.

76
00:08:01,219 --> 00:08:03,761
der lerer Gimant iz geven der lerer fun matematik.

77
00:08:04,442 --> 00:08:09,771
un er hot gehat a min shvakhkeyt tsum shlogn di kinder. er hot gehat

78
00:08:09,771 --> 00:08:19,888
er flegt hobn bay zikh a ⟨lineyke⟩ un baym onfang arop flegt er muzn gebn yedn eynem a zets mitn ⟨milyeyke⟩ oyfn ponem. nit eyn mol hob ikh shoyn gehat fun im gekrogn azelkhene z- azelkhene klep.

79
00:08:19,888 --> 00:08:27,876
un mir hobn zikh fun dest vegn baklogt far far Kharitn vegn dem az der s'iz nit keyn pedagogisher metod mit di kinder.

80
00:08:28,084 --> 00:08:31,925
un mir hobn farshtraykt. in a gutn tog zenen mir kegn gekumen,

81
00:08:32,033 --> 00:08:34,595
s'iz undz gelungen tsu organizirn dem gantsn klas,

82
00:08:34,595 --> 00:08:38,675
un mir zaynen nit gekumen tsum lernen oyf zayn oyf zayn lektsye.

83
00:08:39,188 --> 00:08:43,620
un mir hobn avekgeshtelt aza min oyfgabe,

84
00:08:43,913 --> 00:08:49,864
oyber der lerer vet mit undz lernen, veln mir in gan- veln mir le- veln mir di gan- di shiler, oyfhern fun lernen in gantsn.

85
00:08:50,207 --> 00:08:58,928
Kharit hot oyfgenumen di delegatsye fun di shtrayker fun di shtrayker un er hot fun dest vegn nokhgegebn undz.

86
00:08:58,928 --> 00:09:02,396
un er hot dem lerer Dimant bafrayt fun der

87
00:09:02,396 --> 00:09:08,479
fun fun ler- un mir hobn gekrogn a nokh a an ander a tsveyter lerer a tsveyter lerer fun fun matematik

88
00:09:08,479 --> 00:09:12,020
velkher hot undz ge- tsu undz shoyn gehat in gantsn an ander tsugang.

89
00:09:12,516 --> 00:09:22,534
azoy hobn mir geendikt dem zekstn klas, ikh hob gevolt zeyer vayter lernen farshteyt zikh,

90
00:09:23,805 --> 00:09:31,410
un ikh hob bashlosn, ikh veys nit mir hobn bashlosn, undzer mishpokhe hot bashlosn mir avektsugebn lernen in a yidishn Komer in yidishe gimnazye.

91
00:09:31,450 --> 00:09:35,038
di eyntsike yidishe gimnazye hot zikh ongerufn Yidishe Komers Gimnazye.

92
00:09:35,483 --> 00:09:38,194
ikh bin ariber in Yidishe Komers, zikh genumen lernen.

93
00:09:38,571 --> 00:09:41,028
dortn hot men mir on- ongenumen on an ekzamen,

94
00:09:41,727 --> 00:09:46,226
un ikh bin arayngegangen UNK in a gantsn a nayer velt, in a velt fun yidish.

95
00:09:47,042 --> 00:09:54,523
di lerer zenen dortn geven, ale lerer velkhe ikh hob nor gekumen in der gimnazye, zenen geven zeyer gute.

96
00:09:54,523 --> 00:09:57,498
mir hobn zey tsu zey gehat a groysn derekh-erets.

97
00:09:57,977 --> 00:10:05,733
fun di lerer gedenk ikh di lererin Tsorfas. Feyge Tsorfas hot zi geheysn.

98
00:10:10,448 --> 00:10:14,216
di shiler hobn ir gerufn 'di fas'. far vos 'di fas'?

99
00:10:14,216 --> 00:10:16,646
vayl ir nomen hot geheysn Tsorfas,

100
00:10:16,646 --> 00:10:21,582
hot men genumen fun der dem tsveytn teyl fun ir familye 'fas'. un zi iz geven zeyer a dike,

101
00:10:21,582 --> 00:10:24,178
zeyer a breyte pleytsike aza min,

102
00:10:24,268 --> 00:10:29,999
un m'hot ir ge- a fas heyst a tun, enlekh tsu a tun, hot ir gerufn, "o di fas geyt".

103
00:10:31,305 --> 00:10:35,096
nor zi iz geven zeyer a guter pedagog. a shtrenge, emes zogndik,

104
00:10:35,406 --> 00:10:40,479
ober zi hot g- zi hot gekent zeyer gut yidishe geshikhte, zi hot gelernt yidish un yidishe geshikhte.

105
00:10:40,907 --> 00:10:47,060
ven di fas flegt arayngeyn in klas, flegn ale zayn vern shtil, keyn eyntsikn vort hot men nit gehert.

106
00:10:47,134 --> 00:10:49,035
a flig flegt zikh nit lozn hern.

107
00:10:49,952 --> 00:10:51,583
ikh gedenk zi flegt zogn,

108
00:10:52,298 --> 00:11:02,968
ver vet vagn haynt nit tsu derhern mayn lektsye? der vort 'vagn' iz fun daytsh a bisl. nor vos, zi hot es andersh, zi hot es zeyer oft dermont. "ver vet vagn haynt tsum ton

109
00:11:02,968 --> 00:11:09,132
zikh nit zi UNK, ver vet haynt zikh vagn nit tsu tsuher- tsuhern tsu mayn lektsye?"

110
00:11:09,308 --> 00:11:18,938
ober zi hot gehat aza min pedagogishn tsugang tsu di kinder, az di kinder hobn ir fun dest vegn zeyer hoyl gehat.

111
00:11:21,002 --> 00:11:30,868
zi hot avekgeshtelt ir tsil oys tsu nemen di kinder un zey oysfiln oy- oys- oy- tsutsugreytn tsu der vayterdikn lernen.

112
00:11:31,397 --> 00:11:38,917
a tsveyte lererke velkhe hot hot zikh mir fargedenkt, iz geven di lererin Khaye Itsikzon.

113
00:11:44,290 --> 00:11:47,288
Itsikzon iz geven a vunderbarer mentsh.

114
00:11:50,365 --> 00:12:01,429
zi hot gelernt mit undz khemye un geografye. Itsikzon flegt arayngeyn in klas,

115
00:12:01,975 --> 00:12:08,584
flegt zi onnemen onrufn yedn eynem fun di shiler mitn, nit mitn familye nomen vi a- di iberike di ale iberike lerer, nor mitn nomen.

116
00:12:08,607 --> 00:12:10,575
"hey, Berke, vos makhstu?

117
00:12:11,357 --> 00:12:16,616
Khaimke zog mir vos bist, vos iz bay di haynt aza min shtimung? vos hot bay dir pasirt haynt in shtub? dertseyl!"

118
00:12:18,276 --> 00:12:23,282
oder, "Meyshke, dos zay nit UNK, az nit vel zikh nemen zikh nemen tsu dir."

119
00:12:24,250 --> 00:12:31,010
ot aza min iz geven di lererke, di lererin, Itsikzon.

120
00:12:32,907 --> 00:12:35,359
ale ki- ale shiler hobn ir zeyer hoyl gehat.

121
00:12:35,359 --> 00:12:40,798
vayl zi iz geven zeyer, zi hot gehat a poshetn tsugang tsu di kinder, a khaverishn tsugang tsu ale ki- tsu ale shiler.

122
00:12:42,255 --> 00:12:46,468
shoyn nokhn krig hob ikh der- hob ikh zikh dervust az zi lebt in Vilne,

123
00:12:47,301 --> 00:12:49,421
zi iz shoyn an eltere froy geven farshteyt zikh,

124
00:12:50,187 --> 00:12:59,243
un zayen- lebndik in Vilne hot zi oykh nit farloyrn, hobn di kinder n- di ge- di gevezene shiler oykh nit farloyrn ir dem kontakt mit ir mit ir libe le- mit zeyer libe lererin.

125
00:12:59,282 --> 00:13:02,617
zi iz shtark gesh- g- iz zi geshtorbn tragish oyf ir bet.

126
00:13:02,843 --> 00:13:08,034
lebn ir zenen geshtanen ire gevezene shiler velkhe hobn ir geholfn mit vos zey hobn nor gekent.

127
00:13:08,395 --> 00:13:10,869
azoy hot zi oysge⟨hoykht⟩ ir eydele neshome.

128
00:13:15,010 --> 00:13:23,930
in nayn un draysikstn yor shoyn, hob ikh gemuzt farloyrn dem farlozn di Komersn lager, far vos?

129
00:13:24,274 --> 00:13:27,339
mir hobn gelebt in zeyer materyel a zeyer a shvere lager,

130
00:13:27,902 --> 00:13:32,284
un der foter iz geblibn arbetsloz,

131
00:13:32,492 --> 00:13:36,446
un ikh bin geven der eyntsiker azoy tsu zogn in shtub

132
00:13:36,446 --> 00:13:40,907
der velkher ken helfn der mishpokhe materyel zikh oystsuhaltn.

133
00:13:41,082 --> 00:13:48,722
ikh bin avek fun der gimnazye un ikh hob zikh ayn gelodnt in a min faktur lager, bay Yafet un Goder.

134
00:13:48,722 --> 00:13:53,243
dos iz geven aza min firme velkhe flegt handlen mit oyslendishe skhoyres.

135
00:13:58,902 --> 00:14:02,085
ikh bin dortn arayn lernen al- arbetn als lern-yingl,

136
00:14:02,783 --> 00:14:08,086
mit dem tsuzog az m'vet mikh fun dortn mit der tsayt vet men mikh vel vel ikh dortn vern a

137
00:14:08,086 --> 00:14:14,859
ongeshtelter, azoy tsu zogn a handls-ongeshtelter, mit a mit a shoyn mit a a rekht fun a

138
00:14:15,456 --> 00:14:22,025
tsu oystsumestn skhoyre shoyn, mit rekht tsum far- farkoyfn di skhoyre, hobn a kontakt mit di mit di

139
00:14:22,025 --> 00:14:25,305
p- mit di ts- koy- koyfer un azoy vayter.

140
00:14:26,037 --> 00:14:35,734
hot gearbet tsuzamen eyner shoyn a elterer fun mir, Bushkes, Shayke Bushkes hot er geheysn.

141
00:14:36,229 --> 00:14:45,234
er iz geven a bruder fun dem barimtn ping-pongist, oder fun s- fun tish- fun tish- tenis.

142
00:14:45,797 --> 00:14:47,529
er iz geven a tshempyon fun di ⟨te⟩.

143
00:14:47,687 --> 00:14:56,574
er hot zikh ale mol oysgefraynt az oykh mayn bruder iz a tshempyon, fun te- ping-pong UNK.

144
00:14:59,432 --> 00:15:05,247
dem Bushkes' foter iz geven shoyn an elterer mentsh, ober er iz geven, shoyn in f- in di fuftsiker,

145
00:15:05,592 --> 00:15:08,454
er hot hoyl gehat zeyer a liberer fun tenis.

146
00:15:08,511 --> 00:15:13,432
er flegt yedn shabes un zuntik flegt er in Monika, in kafe Monika,

147
00:15:13,590 --> 00:15:22,005
flegn dortn zayn ovntn tants-ovntn. un er der der elterer mentsh, shoyn a in in di yorn,

148
00:15:22,213 --> 00:15:26,172
flegt nemen, flegt bakumen brivn far zayne tents.

149
00:15:28,592 --> 00:15:37,732
un vayter shoyn arbetndik bay Yafet un Goder, hob ikh zikh bakent mit di yidishe arbeter yugnt.

150
00:15:38,194 --> 00:15:45,376
fun di yidishe sport organizatsyes, di Ska iz geven, Zevaydzhde, Poligrafye, ikh fleg dortn oft araynkumen.

151
00:15:51,103 --> 00:15:59,045
un ikh hob ongehoybn farshteyn dem arbeter lebn.

152
00:16:00,385 --> 00:16:03,602
der arbeter lebn iz geven a shvere in Lite, in amolike Lite.

153
00:16:04,873 --> 00:16:16,072
un di yidishe yugnt hot, a groyser teyl fun der yidishe yugnt, hot ont- iber hoypt fun di sport organizatsyes, flegn onteyl nemen in di untererdishe komyugishe organizatsyes.

154
00:16:16,095 --> 00:16:20,814
ikh hob zikh bakent mit a yat, Avemke Lan,

155
00:16:21,343 --> 00:16:31,327
velkher hot mir tsugezogt az er vet mir onnemen in der untererdisher Moker organizatsye.

156
00:16:32,835 --> 00:16:37,621
nor vos, ikh da- ikh zol darfn oysfirn di ale oysgabes vos di organizatsye shtelt far mir for.

157
00:16:37,577 --> 00:16:40,710
vos iz dos iz geven far an organizatsye, Moker?

158
00:16:40,345 --> 00:16:44,152
Moper iz geven an organizatsye, zi flegt zamlen

159
00:16:44,209 --> 00:16:50,514
bay di bay zamlen bay di arbeter oder bay di bafelkerung gelt,

160
00:16:50,571 --> 00:16:55,746
oystsuhaltn di politishe arestirte in di litvishe tfises, in di litvishe turmes.

161
00:16:57,372 --> 00:17:02,530
di gelt, dos heyst, zey flegn mit dem, zenen v- zey flegn farkoyfn kleyninke

162
00:17:02,637 --> 00:17:08,772
kleyninke fotografyes azelkhene fun farshidene sovetishe firer, Pike Mashenko, Vrashirov,

163
00:17:09,926 --> 00:17:17,362
un di gelt un f- un di gelt farn farn far di kleyne fotokartishkes, flegt men zam- flegt men tsunoyf kloybn

164
00:17:17,875 --> 00:17:22,223
un koyfn produktn far di politishe arestirte in di turmes.

165
00:17:24,507 --> 00:17:30,694
ikh hob mayne oyfgabn oysgefirt. ikh fleg farkoyfn kleyninke fotokartishkes bay mayne khaveyrim, bay mayne bakante, shkheynim,

166
00:17:31,459 --> 00:17:34,746
un der zelber Avremke Lan, hot mir, hot farshtanen

167
00:17:34,746 --> 00:17:39,789
az er, ikh hob gekrogn bay im a a groysn tsutroy, er hot mir gegebn in a gutn,

168
00:17:39,913 --> 00:17:47,147
in a gevisn tog zogt er tsu mir, "ikh hob komunistishe proklamatsyes, m'darf zey oys klebn."

169
00:17:48,233 --> 00:17:52,904
nu di arbet farshteyt zikh iz geven a rizike, vayl in yener tsayt far proklamatsyes flegt men kenen araynzetsn in turme,

170
00:17:52,904 --> 00:17:54,707
nor ikh bin shoyn geven in aza min gayst,

171
00:17:55,000 --> 00:17:59,246
ikh bin geven tsuzamen tsvishn di yidishe arbeter yugnt un ikh hob bashlosn ikh vil dos ton.

172
00:17:59,674 --> 00:18:07,008
ikh hob genumen mayne a khaverte, Shifre Goldin,

173
00:18:08,145 --> 00:18:13,795
un bay nakht, tsvelf a zeyger, zaynen mir hobn mir genumen di proklamatsyes bay Avremke Lan,

174
00:18:13,795 --> 00:18:16,846
un mir zenen klebn di proklamatsyes ibern shtot.

175
00:18:18,287 --> 00:18:22,500
mir hobn oysgek- hobn mir oysgeklebt zeyer fil proklamatsyes in di arbeter kvartarn merstn teyl,

176
00:18:22,624 --> 00:18:28,642
un ven mir zenen tsugegangen tsu Mayroyne gas, tsum ort tsu dem ort vu mir hobn ge- vu ikh hob gearbet bay Yafet un Gon- un Goder,

177
00:18:28,716 --> 00:18:41,215
hot mayn narisher seykhl gezogt tsuge- geb- bay bay meyn narisher seykhl hot mir ge- ge- ge- ge⟨kirt⟩ ikh zol nemen di iberike di ko- proklamatsyes un oysklebn oyf undzer tir vu ikh hob gearbet.

178
00:18:41,811 --> 00:18:43,897
un mir hobn es oysgeklebt di proklamatsyes.

179
00:18:45,102 --> 00:18:50,411
biz undz zen- un bay nakht zenen mir avek, mir hobn geendikt oysklebn, zenen mir zikh funandergegangen aheym.

180
00:18:50,704 --> 00:18:52,892
oyf morgn, ikh kum tsu geyn tsu der arbet,

181
00:18:56,037 --> 00:19:00,452
der balebos fun der fun lager, fun dem kom-mayn faktur lager, Goder,

182
00:19:00,492 --> 00:19:05,953
un der ongeshtelter Shayke Dushkes, hot bamerkt di proklamatsyes hengen oyfn tir,

183
00:19:07,461 --> 00:19:11,589
zey hobn glaykh es aruntergerisn, un zey hobn oyf keyn fal nit

184
00:19:11,882 --> 00:19:15,875
farshtanen az dos iz geven mayn arbet. zey hobn nor tsu mir gezogt, "hey, Meyshl,

185
00:19:15,915 --> 00:19:21,545
du bist dokh a nit keyn narisher yung, ikh halt az du farnemst zikh nit mit azelkhene avantures.

186
00:19:22,311 --> 00:19:23,773
nor zolstu visn zayn,

187
00:19:24,083 --> 00:19:27,522
oyber mir veln khapn di velkhe hobn dos ongeklebt, vet zey

188
00:19:27,522 --> 00:19:33,071
veln zey fun dem veln zey bay ⟨undzet⟩ veln mir zey zikh mit zey zikh gut oprekhenen."

189
00:19:33,837 --> 00:19:41,486
ikh hob gants zikh ayngehaltn fun gelekhter, vayl ikh hob oy- ikh hob es ikh hob ikh hob zikh farshtanen ikh hob dokh farshtanen s'mayn arbet.

190
00:19:41,486 --> 00:19:42,740
nor ikh hob gemuzt shvaygn.

191
00:19:44,923 --> 00:19:54,148
nu, do in vayter ken ikh forzetsn tsu dertseyln vegn mayn vayterdikn lebn.

192
00:19:57,478 --> 00:20:05,811
in eyn un fertsikstn yor, iz arayn di Royte Armey in Kovne. in Kaunes. in Kaunes.

193
00:20:03,882 --> 00:20:06,294
shoyn in fertsikstn.

194
00:20:05,811 --> 00:20:08,727
in fertsikstn yor, in in fertsikstn yor, di Royte Armey gor.

195
00:20:14,151 --> 00:20:19,733
emes zogndik, di yidishe arbeter yugnt un di yidishe arbertershaft

196
00:20:19,733 --> 00:20:23,158
hobn gehat a groysn paket fun di Royte Armey. far vos?

197
00:20:23,158 --> 00:20:32,622
vayl zey hobn gehoft az di Royte Armey vet oysglaykhn azoy tsu zogn dem di natsyonale rekht fun di yidn in Lite. un

198
00:20:33,405 --> 00:20:36,960
un efsher vet gelingen zikh materyel beser aynordenen.

199
00:20:37,303 --> 00:20:42,900
mir hobn oyfgenum- oyfgenumen di Royte Armey zeyer mit a groys libe.

200
00:20:43,598 --> 00:20:47,119
ikh hob zikh arayngevorfn glaykh in der arbet fun fun komyug,

201
00:20:49,082 --> 00:20:53,632
un mir hot men, di ershte arbet vos ikh gedenk

202
00:20:53,925 --> 00:20:58,250
iz geven mir hobn onteyl genumen in di er- in di ershte valn vos iz forgekumen.

203
00:20:58,250 --> 00:21:06,426
oys tsu oys tsu oystsuva- oys tsu veln a nayem a nayem seym. a folks-seym azoy tsu zogn in Lite.

204
00:21:06,426 --> 00:21:07,903
ikh bin geven a agitator.

205
00:21:07,903 --> 00:21:23,737
mit mir hobn gearbet in dem in di ge- in di agit-brigade azelkhene khevre vi Leyzer Zilber, Rifke Levit,

206
00:21:26,427 --> 00:21:32,309
der eltster fun der ki- agit-brigade iz geven Meyshke Muslis, a kumendiker

207
00:21:32,468 --> 00:21:35,246
partizan, velkher mir hobn zikh mit im getrofn in geto.

208
00:21:37,362 --> 00:21:43,971
mir flegn geyn iber di iber di shtiber iber di voynung un agitirn far di sovyetn makht,

209
00:21:43,993 --> 00:21:48,941
tsuzogn di ale tsuzogn di ale aynvoyner az s'vet kumen, zey zoln shtimen far di sovyetn makht

210
00:21:48,963 --> 00:21:52,022
un s'vet di o makht velkhe, di arbeter makht,

211
00:21:52,022 --> 00:21:57,993
veln mir veln zikh gi- vet zikh farshteyt zikh gikh beser far- far- -besern di zeyer materyele lage.

212
00:21:57,993 --> 00:22:03,489
mir zenen nokh geven dan yunge kinder, in zibetsn akhtsn yor, naive khevre,

213
00:22:03,489 --> 00:22:12,978
un mir hobn zey tsugezogt afile az m'vet zey kri- zey veln krign naye voynungen, mir veln zey bashteln krign naye mebl, zoln zey nor geyn shtimen far der far farn seym.

214
00:22:14,706 --> 00:22:16,573
nor s'gekumen der tog fun di valn,

215
00:22:16,883 --> 00:22:23,486
gedenk ikh, ho'mir zikh oysgeshtelt oyf di di gantse gas velkhe undzer undzer rayon velkhe mir hobn agitirt,

216
00:22:23,486 --> 00:22:27,086
ho'mir zikh oysgeshtelt oyfn gas un mir zenen gegangen kolektiv,

217
00:22:27,717 --> 00:22:31,797
in der ershte ray iz ge- zenen mir gegangen bin ikh gegangen ikh mit a royte fone,

218
00:22:31,797 --> 00:22:34,683
Meyshke Mushes iz gegangen mit a groysn presparent,

219
00:22:34,683 --> 00:22:40,217
un Rivka Levit iz gegangen mit, gedenk ikh, mit a

220
00:22:40,217 --> 00:22:46,526
oykh mit a fone ongeshribn, "mir geyen shtimen far undzer arbeter regirung."

221
00:22:52,050 --> 00:22:54,710
shoyn nokh di valn, in fertsikstn yor,

222
00:22:56,775 --> 00:23:01,241
zayendik als komyugist un nokh a umlegaler komyugist, hot men mir bashtimt

223
00:23:02,142 --> 00:23:04,028
ikh gedenk shoyn nisht ver s'hot mir bashtimt,

224
00:23:04,028 --> 00:23:09,543
nor mir hot gedukht az in handls- azoy vi ikh bin geven a in handls- arb- in in handls-rayo- opteylung

225
00:23:09,600 --> 00:23:16,614
hot men mir bashtimt als farvalter fun a magazin, f- fun a produktovn magazin.

226
00:23:17,312 --> 00:23:19,095
ikh bin dan geven in gantsn

227
00:23:19,489 --> 00:23:26,064
dos iz geven in fertsikstn yor, umgefer ken men zibetsn yor, zekhtsn zibetsn yor, als farvalter fun a magazin.

228
00:23:26,188 --> 00:23:31,178
ikh hob mit freyd oyfgenumen di arbet. ikh bin gekumen tsu geyn dem magazin,

229
00:23:31,285 --> 00:23:36,020
un ikh hob glaykh gegebn farsheydene onvayzungen vi tsum firn der arbet.

230
00:23:36,415 --> 00:23:43,647
nor vos, keyn keyn ikh hob nit gehat keyn keyn keyn farshteyt zikh keyn keyn keyn anung vi azoy tsum firn mit der arbet.

231
00:23:44,548 --> 00:23:49,773
derbay iz gezesn, ikh hob dort gehat in dem magazin a kasir, velkher hot hoyl gehat oystsutrinken,

232
00:23:49,898 --> 00:23:55,328
un un ven ikh fleg ir nit bamerkn,

233
00:23:55,328 --> 00:23:59,365
flegt er farbay geyn ale mol dem vinkl vu s'geshtanen dortn di fleshlekh mit branfn

234
00:23:59,365 --> 00:24:04,013
un er flegt ale mol araynleygn a shtikl a b- a a f- a fleshl branfn in keshene, dos.

235
00:24:04,225 --> 00:24:08,961
ikh hob dos ersht nit bamerkt. nor shpeter hob ikh bamerkt az s'gevorn epes pust in dem vinkl.

236
00:24:13,033 --> 00:24:15,069
farn hant hob ikh im keyn mol nit gekhapt.

237
00:24:15,379 --> 00:24:21,296
un hot oysgekumen a revizye. a revizye fun dem handls-opteylung.

238
00:24:22,095 --> 00:24:25,312
der onfirer fun handls-opteylung iz geven Shtrum, gedenk ikh.

239
00:24:27,934 --> 00:24:30,830
er hot geshikt a revizye in undzer magazin a kuk ton vi men

240
00:24:30,853 --> 00:24:35,015
tu- kontrolirn mayn arbet. ikh arbet Geguzhinski als farvalter fun a magazin.

241
00:24:35,646 --> 00:24:44,240
farshteyt zikh az in oyfnemendik makhndik a revizye, hot zikh ba- hot zikh bakumen az es felt zeyer fil

242
00:24:44,240 --> 00:24:50,645
zeyer fil skhoyre, dos heyst oyf a gevi- s'aray- in a groysn defitsit bin ikh arayngegangen, derfar vos

243
00:24:50,645 --> 00:24:53,865
der der kasirer hot bay flegt bay mir oystrinken di gantse branfn.

244
00:24:54,462 --> 00:24:56,380
tsveytns iz geven aza min zakh.

245
00:24:57,027 --> 00:24:59,906
ikh hob genumen prod- fleg bashteln produktn,

246
00:24:59,946 --> 00:25:05,764
velkhe ikh hob nit gehat keyn keyn in dem keyn anung velkhe produktn, vo- vos far a vifl zey tsu haltn,

247
00:25:05,764 --> 00:25:08,866
ikh gedenk az dortn iz geven in in magazin vursht.

248
00:25:09,497 --> 00:25:13,017
di vursht iz geven frishe, zey flegn lign bay mir

249
00:25:13,092 --> 00:25:17,855
etlekhe teg oder a gantse vokh tsayt. keyn koyfer zenen azoy nit geven. zey zenen gevorn alt,

250
00:25:17,855 --> 00:25:20,864
un zey zoln gebn tsum foylns, ikh hob genumen hern fun zey.

251
00:25:21,107 --> 00:25:25,134
di revizye hot dos alts gekhapt un alts farshri- far- far- farfiksirt.

252
00:25:25,647 --> 00:25:34,449
un men hot mir tsugeshtelt a khezhbm az es felt bay mir iber toyznt mit tsvey hundert lit.

253
00:25:35,991 --> 00:25:39,303
ikh hob zikh dershrokn, vos kumt do for, vos zol ikh do itster makhn?

254
00:25:39,303 --> 00:25:42,295
m'hot mir oysgerufn in handls-opteylung, bay dem Shtrumen,

255
00:25:42,724 --> 00:25:47,797
un m'hot mir gezogt, "ey, du bist, vos, vi kumt bay dir tsu zayn in aza min defitsit?

256
00:25:48,462 --> 00:25:51,796
du vest bay undz keyn farvalter shoyn mer nit zayn."

257
00:25:52,022 --> 00:25:55,610
un ikh hob farshtanen az anshtot mir hot men shoyn gehat tsugegreyt a tsveytn.

258
00:25:55,684 --> 00:26:01,022
dos iz geven di revizye iz gemakht gevorn shpetsyel kedey tsu tsu avektsushteln an- anshtot mir a tsveyte froy.

259
00:26:01,022 --> 00:26:03,123
di froy fun, di familye fun di froy gedenk ikh nit,

